    "en": {
      "title": "Will Kota enter politics?; Namal's answer",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Getting involved in politics? Isn't it? Member of Parliament Namal Rajapaksa said that former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa should decide.",
        "Former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa has the right to return to the country as a citizen of Sri Lanka. Similarly, Kota should decide whether to join politics or not.",
        "He also said that Gotabaya Rajapaksa should first decide what to do in the future."
      ],
